title: Garmin Cyclops Safety Camera All Countries
description:
Safety camera poi for Garmin devices.  Already unlocked just drop into your Garmin/POI folder or sd/Garmin/POI  Then turn on your device, go to Tools> Settings> Proximity Points> Change and make sure the box marked Garmin Safety Cameras is checked.  That should be it. 

I am not sure what devices this works on, I have Nuvi 7x5 series and it works just fine.  I would check the Garmin website for a full list.

THIS IS CURRENT AS OF DEC 09 2015
